DB[560814]={D="Réduit le temps de recharge de Poussée d'adrénaline de 30 secondes.",DE="Reduces the cooldown of Adrenaline Rush by 30 sec.",N="Pied sûr"}
DB[560822]={D="Réduit le temps de recharge de |cffffffffLancer de Glaive|r de $/1000;s1 sec et augmente sa durée de $/1000;s2 sec.",DE="When Hateforged Barrier is removed from you, you now reduce 10% of all Magic damage taken for 8 sec.\nIn addition, Hateforged Barrier now heals for an additional 2% of your maximum health each tick.",N="Antimagie"}
