DB[560910]={D="|cffffffffCarnage maximum|r augmente désormais la vitesse de déplacement de $560909s1% et vous rend immunisé contre les effets de réduction de mouvement pendant $560909d.",DE="Increases the duration of Maximum Carnage by 1 sec and it now grants Utter Devastation for 6 sec.\nUtter Devastation\nInstantly removes all movement impairing effects, increases your movement speed by 25%, and makes you immune to slows.\nCan be consumed by Decapitate or Crush to guarantee them to critically strike.",N="Dévastation totale"}
