aura(560977, "Casting Horrorbolt now grants Inspired Malice for 12 sec.\nInspired Malice\nYour next Gaze of C'thun, Darkwither or Wrath of the Black Empire will be empowered.\nGaze of C'thun: Critical strike chance increased by 20%.\nDarkwither: Shadow damage dealt increased by 5% and damage of Darkwither by an additional 15% for 10 sec.\nWrath of the Black Empire: Deals 25% increased damage.", "|cFFFFFFFFEldritch Blast|r génère maintenant jusqu'à $560978u piles de Chuchotements dans l'ombre. À $560978u piles, vous gagnez |cFFFFFFFFInspired Malice|r.\n@s:560979@")
aura(560992, "Reduces the cooldown of Warpdagger by 5 sec.", "Réduit le temps de recharge de Warpdagger de 5 secondes.")
