DB[561069]={D="Apprend |cffffffffLancer de potion|r et |cffffffffIngrédient : Champignons de la jungle|r.@s:801661:0@@s:801660:0@",DE="You can now add an additional Ingredient to your Cauldron, enhancing your brew.\nTeaches you Ingredient: Fish Oil.\nIngredient: Fish Oil\nBrew Fish Oil into your Cauldron.\nCauldron: Increases the movement speed and swim speed of allies within 40 yds by 10%.\nPotion: Increases the target ally's movement speed by 20% and dodge chance by 5% for 8 sec.",N="Mixologue"}
